</Resource></Resources><Commentaries><Commentary id="key-00b6ab73c5488716bfd945c2c08db8d2" Type="F"><Para><Text>Sch. 4 para. 7(3A) inserted (28.4.2014) by <Citation URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/597" id="rnb8sic5-d3e41625a1310" Class="UnitedKingdomStatutoryInstrument" Year="2014" Number="597" Title="The Universal Credit and Miscellaneous Amendments Regulations 2014">The Universal Credit and Miscellaneous Amendments Regulations 2014 (S.I. 2014/597)</Citation>, <CitationSubRef CitationRef="rnb8sic5-d3e41625a1310" id="rnb8sic5-d3e41628a1310" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/597/regulation/1" SectionRef="regulation-1">regs. 1</CitationSubRef>, <CitationSubRef CitationRef="rnb8sic5-d3e41625a1310" id="rnb8sic5-d3e41631a1310" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/597/regulation/2/13/c" SectionRef="regulation-2-13-c" Operative="true">2(13)(c)</CitationSubRef></Text></Para></Commentary><Commentary id="key-715e01ad493375dea4f393df92aab21a" Type="F"><Para><Text>Sch. 4 para. 7(2)(aa) inserted (28.4.2014) by <Citation URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/597" id="rnb8sic5-d3e46646a1310" Class="UnitedKingdomStatutoryInstrument" Year="2014" Number="597" Title="The Universal Credit and Miscellaneous Amendments Regulations 2014">The Universal Credit and Miscellaneous Amendments Regulations 2014 (S.I. 2014/597)</Citation>, <CitationSubRef CitationRef="rnb8sic5-d3e46646a1310" id="rnb8sic5-d3e46649a1310" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/597/regulation/1" SectionRef="regulation-1">regs. 1</CitationSubRef>, <CitationSubRef CitationRef="rnb8sic5-d3e46646a1310" id="rnb8sic5-d3e46652a1310" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2014/597/regulation/2/13/a" SectionRef="regulation-2-13-a" Operative="true">2(13)(a)</CitationSubRef></Text></Para></Commentary><Commentary id="key-8ba2d51af5a2fd5ca2f5844ce7150062" Type="F"><Para><Text>Words in Sch. 4 para. 7(3) inserted (28.4.2014) by <Citation URI="http://www.legislation.gov.